metadata.name: Trap Nap
metadata.description:
A piece identifying the mess of a life I was living.

Sofa Surfing, pushing everyone close to me further away, doing anything to get me to the next day but also killing myself daily with the Alcohol and Drug intake not knowing if Iâ€™ll see the next day!

Now Clean of it all I look back and feel Warm inside that I can recreate my Trauma now I have overcome it, and potentially help others overcome theirs.
